        <abstract> 
<p>Recommends Leonard Horner’s "Account of some recent researches near Cairo" for publication in <hi rend="italic">Philosophical Transactions</hi> [<hi rend="italic">R. Soc. Lond.</hi> 148 (1858): 53–9]. Believes all the details and sections should be published in full because of importance of investigations leading to the conclusion that man has existed in Egypt for over 13000 years.</p> 
